HadoopCodecFactory - Class in org.apache.avro.hadoop.file
Encapsulates the ability to specify and configure an avro compression codec from a given hadoop codec defined with the configuration parameter: mapred.output.compression.codec Currently there are three codecs registered by default: org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.DeflateCodec will map to deflate org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.SnappyCodec will map to snappy org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.BZip2Codec will map to zbip2 org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.GZipCodec will map to deflate
